    "body": "On macOS, `test_bitcoin-qt` has skipped `AppTests`, `WalletTests`, and `AddressBookTests` under the `minimal` QPA plugin since https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/commit/a3197c5294df4711bab0ff6dcdd061ceab115c7d (2018, Qt 5.11), pointing to [QTBUG-49686](https://qt-project.atlassian.net/browse/QTBUG-49686).\r\n\r\nThe recent re-evaluation of the Bitcoin Core codebase showed that the Qt bug report is no longer relevant. The remaining causes were in our own code, and they are fixed in the first commit.",
